name: RouteStatus
description: The status of a route. The status can be pending, processing, done, not_found or error

enumValues.name: pending
enumValues.description: Route is queued and pending processing. Temporary status

enumValues.name: processing
enumValues.description: We are computing the route for your request. Temporary status

enumValues.name: done
enumValues.description: We finished computing the route, with a result. Final status

enumValues.name: not_found
enumValues.description: We finished the computing the route, without any result. Final status

enumValues.name: error
enumValues.description: An error occurred while computing the route. Final status
